body_html:
We expect smaller latency values with TFLite if you follow the blogpost instructions (~15fps):
https://medium.com/tensorflow/training-and-serving-a-realtime-mobile-object-detector-in-30-minutes-with-cloud-tpus-b78971cf1193

You may use any of the mobilenet ssd checkpoints with the instructions above.
